lead_paragraph: MotoGP world champion Marc Marquez set the fastest lap in practice for the Malaysian Grand Prix on Friday despite missing the second session due to a bout of gastroenteritis.

headline.print_headline: Motorcycling: Marquez Resting After Stomach Bug at Sepang
